    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><strong>Role and appointment </strong></p>
<p>Every programme must have an external examiner. This person will:</p>
<ul>
<li>provide an independent check on marking and academic standards;</li>
<li>provide advice on assessment and the curriculum;</li>
<li>submit an annual report indicating their impression of the programme’s strengths and areas for development.</li>
</ul>]]></Value>
